The Proposal:
Arya Chanakya Vidyadham School run by Rajarshi Shahu Institute of Education and Village Industries, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar
Jatwara, T.G. Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar, a Marathi medium unaided secondary (e.g. 5th to 10th)
Transfer of management of the school to Rashtra Dharma Sanskar Prabodhini Sanstha, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar.
The proposal received under the reference letter was under the consideration of the government.
The government's decision:
The school is managed by the Rashtra Dharma Sanskar Prabodhini Sanstha, Chhatrapati Sambhajinagar.
The Government has decided to approve the transfer on the following terms and conditions: -
(1) The condition of minimum marks of the school where the management has changed shall be relaxed for any reason.
